<style>
    /* Global Styles */
    body {
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        background-color: #f8f8f8;
        color: #333;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
    }

    /* Body Styles */
    .body-container {
        padding: 20px;
    }

    .sender-name {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .message-content {
        font-size: 16px;
    }

    .confirmation-link {
        color: #007bff;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: bold;
    }

</style>

<!-- Body -->
<div class="body-container">
    <p class="sender-name">Dear {{name}},</p>
    <p class="message-content">
        Welcome to our community! We are delighted to have you on board. To ensure the security of your account, please click the confirmation link below:
        <br><br>
        <a class="confirmation-link" href="{{link}}" target="_blank">Confirm Your Account</a>
        <br><br>
        If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out to our support team at {{support_email}}.
        <br><br>
        Thank you for choosing [company]. We look forward to providing you with a seamless and rewarding experience.
    </p>
</div>
